net.proteusframework.cms.component.generator

Interface DelegateRenderer<T extends PageElement>

  • Type Parameters:
    T - the page element type.
    All Superinterfaces:
    Renderer<T>
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    MIWTGenerator, MIWTRenderer

    public interface DelegateRenderer<T extends PageElement>
extends Renderer<T>
    A renderer that is delegated to. This is typically used in places where code reuse is desired and the interaction with the request is encapsulated.

    CMS is not designed to allow linking to / targeting delegated renderers (via delegated ContentElements or DelegateRenderers).

    Author:
    Russ Tennant (russ@i2rd.com)
